paragraphs.text: you and i walk a fragile line. i have known it all this time. but i never thought i'd live to see it break. it's getting dark and it's all too quiet and i can't trust anything now. and it's coming over you like it's all a big mistake.
oh, holding my breath. won't lose you again. something's made your eyes go cold.
